title: APT ORB / electrochem after picking up speed
description: Upon picking up the speed, electrochem chimes in. Needs a wa to go away if you give it up to cuno or take it yourself?

dialogueTree.title: Electrochemistry: "Take the speed. Take that glorious..."
dialogueTree.english: Take the speed. Take that glorious stuff. You have it now. You've got it! TAKE IT!
dialogueTree.polish: Weź speed. Weź ten wspaniały towar. Masz go. Masz go! WIĘC GO WEŹ!
dialogueTree.belarusian: Вазьмі спід. Вазьмі гэты цудоўны тавар. У цябе ёсць ён. У цябе ёсць ён! ДЫ ВАЗЬМІ Ж ЯГО!

links.title: Electrochemistry: "FUCKING RIGHT! PUT THAT BOTTLE IN Y..."
links.english: FUCKING RIGHT! PUT THAT BOTTLE IN YOUR HAND AND PARTY DOWN!
links.polish: TAK, KURWA! BIERZ TĘ BUTELKĘ W ŁAPSKO I KRĘCIMY IMPREZĘ!
links.belarusian: ТАК, БЛЯ! БЯРЫ ГЭТУ БУТЭЛЮ Ў РУКУ І ПАЧЫНАЕМ ВЕЧАРЫНКУ!

links.title: You: "No. Not right now, anyway. [Discard..."
links.english: No. Not right now, anyway. [Discard thought.]
links.polish: Nie. W każdym razie nie teraz. [Odrzuć myśl].
links.belarusian: Не. У любым выпадку не зараз. [Адхіліць думку].

links.title: Electrochemistry: "Come on. Come on! A little! Just a..."
links.english: Come on. Come on! A little! Just a little bit! Whaddya say, huh?
links.polish: No daj spokój. Tylko trochę! Odrobinę! Malutką! Co powiesz? No?
links.belarusian: Ну, супакойся. Толькі трохі! Крыху! Малюсенькую! Што скажаш? Ну?

links.title: Electrochemistry: "Just a little. Then a lot. Come on,..."
links.english: Just a little. Then a lot. Come on, party boy! Let's get FUCKED!
links.polish: Tylko troszkę. A potem dużo. No dalej, imprezowiczu! Czas się SKOTŁOWAĆ!
links.belarusian: Толькі крыху. А потым шмат. Ну давай, гулец! Час ЗАВАРУШЫЦЦА!

links.title: You: "I said I discard the thought! [Disc..."
links.english: I said I discard the thought! [Discard thought.]
links.belarusian: Я сказаў, што адкідваю думку! [Адкінь думку].

links.title: Electrochemistry: "Fuck you. You used to be cool. Why..."
links.english: Fuck you. You used to be cool. Why can't you just take the bottle and snort snort snort?
links.polish: A pierdol się. Kiedyś byłeś czadowy. Czemu nie możesz po prostu wziąć tej butelki i się sztachać, sztachać, sztachać?
links.belarusian: Ідзі на х... Калісьці ты быў класным. Чаму ты не можаш проста ўзяць гэтую бутэльку і зацягвацца, зацягвацца, зацягвацца?
